<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Pin Validation</title>
    <style>
        /* Add your custom styles here */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }

        p {
            color: #666666;
        }

        .pin-container {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #888888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Email Pin Validation</h1>
        <p>Your pin for validation is:</p>

        <div class="pin-container">
            <strong><%= pin %></strong>
        </div>

        <p>Please use this pin to validate your email address.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for using our services.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>